extracted_content.content:
[![Image 1: Smith.ai Logo](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5b15ca3d02dd414c89ecc3ed/649a3c37ed83f26f7363dfcf_Logo.svg)](https://smith.ai/)

Convert conversations to clients
--------------------------------

AI-first voice answering, backed by professional human agents, 24/7.

##### Starter

30 calls

$97.50 / month

### Basic

90 calls

$270.00 / month

### Pro

300 calls

$825.00 / month

### Enterprise

Custom

Ask about enterprise pricing

#### ALL PLANS INCLUDE A 14-DAY MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE, PLUS:

Lead screening, qualification & intake

Live expert agents on standby 24/7

Rich business insights in your dashboard

No setup fees

No annual contracts

No hidden fees

No charge for spam

### What’s in the box?

Core features included in every AI Receptionist plan, no matter your call volume.

##### Included features

Lead qualification

We’ll capture and qualify your leads based on your custom criteria.

Leads are screened to determine if they are a good fit based on needs, location, and budget.

Free!

New client intake

We’ll ask business-specific intake questions for your qualified leads.

Up to 10 short-answer questions (e.g., case number, car model, dog breed.)

Free!

Call transfers

Assign transfer destinations to efficiently route calls.

Set unique transfer destinations for different caller types.

Free!

Escalate to human agent

Our 24/7 North America-based agents are available for complex matters.

Calls of an intricate nature or requests for live-support are automatically routed to our agents.

Free!

Appointment booking

We’ll book appointments on your calendar of choice, live on the call.

Smith.ai works with any calendaring platform that provides a direct link to the appointment.

Free!

Dedicated phone number

A local or toll-free number is given to you, and only you.

You'll have a dedicated number to use for calls. Or port your business number at no charge.

Free!

Call recording & transcription

We’ll automatically record and transcribe all calls.

Includes access to call recordings, searchable transcripts & PII masking. [Learn more.](https://docs.smith.ai/article/fzv1b69n7t-call-recording-transcription-with-smith-ai)

Free!

Answer caller questions

Provide clear, helpful answers to your callers’ most common questions.

Add up to 50 custom Q&A pairs to ensure your callers get the information they need.

Free!

Instant call summaries

Get summaries sent to the tools you already use — email, Slack & Teams.

Respond to leads faster and keep your team informed after every call.

Free!

### Smith.ai is trusted by 3,000+ businesses

![Image 2](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5b15ca3d02dd414c89ecc3ed/649a4be2c72d3464af8bbfbf_logo_white_CLUTCH.svg)

5.0 stars

![Image 3](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5b15ca3d02dd414c89ecc3ed/649a4be2c72d3464af8bbfc0_Group%202160.svg)

4.9 stars

![Image 4](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5b15ca3d02dd414c89ecc3ed/649a4be2c72d3464af8bbfbe_capterra_logo.svg)

5.0 stars

![Image 5](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5b15ca3d02dd414c89ecc3ed/649a4be2c72d3464af8bbfc2_Trustpilot.svg)

4.8 stars

##### Converts callers into clients

Smith.ai is our inbound sales team. Having a trained and personable voice has transformed our ability to answer the phone and convert callers to clients.

[Read case study](https://smith.ai/case-studies/cmit-solutions-downtown-chicago)

##### Frequently asked questions

Our AI answering service costs a little bit more because it does a lot more. Unlike others offering AI that stops at answering basic questions (assuming they even get them right, which most don’t), you can trust us with your business’ reputation. First, we have humans in the loop. With our AI Receptionist, your calls are always handled by our AI first, but if something complex comes up, the call can be transferred to a live North America-based receptionist — any time, day or night. This built-in human backup ensures your callers get the help they need while you never get interrupted. It's the perfect blend of efficiency and reliability. Second, our system is designed specifically to qualify your leads based on our industry-leading experience answering over 10 million calls for businesses in the past 10 years. So yes, it’s a bit pricier than the competition — because we’re committed to making every interaction exceptional.

No. Smith.ai does not charge for spam calls — as long as we can block them in the future. If you use a forwarding service but disable Caller ID pass-through (common with Google Voice clients), we won’t be able to block them, and thus you will be charged for those calls. You can learn more about this [here](https://docs.smith.ai/article/t5ba81iu37-article-36-why-we-need-caller-id).

With technology! Our system automatically blocks over 20 million spam and robocalls from ever getting through. If a new spam number does get through, you can mark it as spam to add it to the spam list so it can’t get through ever again.

No. AI Receptionist is a month-to-month service. This means there aren’t any long-term contracts. You pay for the AI Receptionist service each month. If you ever cancel, we need 30 days' notice, and then you’re done. And we will miss you.

Yes, at any time. We make it easy. If you would like to change your plan, just email [support@smith.ai](mailto:support@smith.ai). We'll start billing for your new plan the next month.

Because unlike per-minute services, our success is aligned with your success. Billing per call means there’s no mystery accounting involved. You’re trusting us to represent your business. We’re optimized for the exact right length of calls, not more or less. Per-minute services work opposite to your needs; they want to maximize your call length while you want to minimize your call time.

Do you want your business to succeed? Well, good. We do, too. A successful business can’t afford to miss a single lead or sales opportunity. (By the time you call them back, they’ve likely found someone else… or if they’re really bad, they’ll leave a negative review because you didn’t answer.) Our AI Receptionist isn’t just another AI; it’s the only one on the market designed specifically for lead qualification and with 24/7 human backup. If a caller needs more than what our AI can handle, they get immediately transferred to a real person to help. No missed calls, no frustrated customers — just flawless support. And here’s the best part: It’s a fraction of the cost of an in-house receptionist, yet it works 24/7 and never takes a lunch break. So, you’re not just paying for an answering service; you’re investing in a solution that’s always on, always reliable, and always working for you.

At Smith.ai we want our services to provide real value for your business and truly take work off your plate. And we want you to be able to fully experience what it’s like to have us on the front lines, risk free. That’s why we offer a 14-day money-back guarantee to all new clients. We get it. Things happen. If you decide Smith.ai isn’t for you in the first two weeks, we’ll refund your initial plan — no strings attached.

To receive your money back, send us your request within 14 days of your subscription date. Please send it via email to [support@smith.ai](mailto:support@smith.ai) with the subject line “Money-Back Request.”

Here are the details:

*   New clients of Smith.ai can get their money back on Starter, Basic, Pro, and Custom plans for 14 days.
*   If you want to cancel your service for any reason in the first 14 days, you get a refund of your plan and any add-on services, regardless of how many calls or chats you have used, up to $1,000.
*   Any calls over your plan quota (“overage”) are not included in the money-back guarantee.  
    

We offer volume discounts and can create a custom plan to suit your high-volume needs. Please [book a free consultation](https://smith.ai/booking-air) with our team.

### Take the faster path to growth.

Get Smith.ai today.

Affordable plans for every budget.

Affordable pricing to enhance your sales & support teams — get superior 24/7 customer engagement services with live North America-based agents.
